        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4198",
        "content": "Little is known regarding his brief reign.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4198_61336_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4198/61336/4198_61336_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4198",
        "content": "Apparently Hoshea, king of Israel, pretended when the Assyrians entered his country that he remained friendly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4198_61336_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4198/61336/4198_61336_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4198",
        "content": "Shalmaneser, however, was well informed, and made Hoshea a prisoner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
